{"tid":981271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】豬Hi利是封？","createTime":"2019-01-14T07:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T07:41:20.000Z","uid":119217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b3dd6e91658c367ff8ec77997806d4d01f8c60","tid":981271,"uid":119217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>【利是封「豬中藏hi」　網民大讚：了解廣州文化】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190114/bkn-20190114125319469-0114_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190114%2Fbkn-20190114125319469-0114_00822_001.html&d=LAkC%2Fxj5WDMblhR9Z6BKdnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a8dd1eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190114/bkn-20190114125319469-0114_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190114/photo/bkn-20190114125319469-0114_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190114130541\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190114125319469-0114_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190114130541&h=de665f7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9243dbe68655088b30ea33bc75822a800083069","tid":981271,"uid":119217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"新年講究意頭，恭賀說話絕不嫌多。本港有律師行響應農曆新年傳統，製作自己品牌的利是封，惟網民一睇，卻發現怪怪的？<br />\n<br />\n2019年是己亥豬年，有律師行已率先派發利是，並以生肖「豬」作主題，在長方形的紅色利是封中間，繪上豬形公仔，以「亥」字描繪豬頭，並在豬身空白位置印上「hi」的字樣。<br />\n<br />\n該利是封引起網民熱議︰「亥、豬、hi，乜咁似粗口」、「呢個正，可能了解過廣州文化先創作得出，派畀啲唔鍾意嘅親戚細路啱晒」，有人又大讚︰「唔計諧音問題，個亥字畫成嘅豬本身意念唔錯」、「我好想要呀」。<br />\n<br />\n《港呢啲》向該律師行查詢事件，正候回覆。"},{"pid":"9a0f1de95c150c0e42b375c03cc17f97dca57814","tid":981271,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"要封利是比你班豬hi條氣就唔L順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241b6a50dfb2be58b46cf94127804493b7912641","tid":981271,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實設計唔錯喎<br />\n個&quot;亥&quot;字畫到豬頭咁幾正丫"}]}